Author: Corey Thompson <coreyt@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat May 30 20:06:05 2026 -0500

    feat(0.7.2): EU-8 IR-recall harness (orthogonal to ANN recall)
    
    Add a relevance-judged IR recall signal alongside ANN recall. Scores engine.search() against externally-labelled relevant doc_ids from chain ground_truth_queries, using the real default embedder. Additive IRQuery + extract_ground_truth_queries in corpus_subset.rs; new eu8_ir_validation.rs (recall/precision/MRR/NDCG@10, body->doc_id first-occurrence map, bootstrap CI, per-relation/per-shape aggregation, diagnostics; AGENT_LONG-gated, EU8_SMOKE small-corpus seam). Corrected design note: EU-8 DOES require --features default-embedder. SMALL-CORPUS SMOKE JSON included. Zero changes to eu7 or engine/embedder/quant/mean.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>

